80819 Calle Azul, La Quinta, CA 92253

About 80819 Calle Azul

A sunlit desert escape in La Quinta's sought-after Puerta Azul community. Casa Calle Azul is a two bedroom hacienda offers private pool and spa, mountain views, and two en-suite bedrooms -- ideal for couples, families, or remote work. Enjoy resort amenities, lush outdoor space, and modern comforts just minutes from Old Town, golf, and hiking. The space From the moment you arrive at Casa Calle Azul, you'll feel the calm of the desert settle in. Located inside the gated Puerta Azul community, this single-level home offering a private, restful setting ideal for couples, families, or friends traveling together. Inside, the layout is open and welcoming. The living room connects effortlessly to a fully equipped kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and everything you need to cook, dine, and feel at home. A half bath is available off the main living area for added convenience. The home features two private en-suite bedrooms, thoughtfully placed on opposite sides of the house for maximum privacy. One has a king bed, the other a queen, each with dual vanities and plenty of room to unpack and settle in. Step outside and you'll find the kind of outdoor space that defines a La Quinta getaway -- a wraparound patio framed by citrus trees and desert landscaping, your own private pool and spa, and a cozy fire pit to gather around at night. You'll also enjoy access to Puerta Azul's resort-style amenities, including: Two community pools and spas A fitness center, tennis court, bocce ball court, and clubhouse Beautiful walking paths and secure, gated entry Additional features include an attached garage, in-unit washer Ring doorbell camera at the front entrance and a camera overlooking the pool area and above the garage. No interior cameras. Whether you're looking for a quiet place to reset or a stylish base for exploring everything La Quinta has to offer, Casa Calle Azul is ready to welcome you. Guest access Our home is dedicated to ensuring your comfort and convenience. You'll find ample space in closets and bathroom drawers to settle in and make yourself at home. Feel free to utilize all the kitchen amenities, but we kindly request that you handle them with care. To ensure a smooth arrival, we'll send you a Welcome Letter one day before your check-in. This letter will provide you with all the essential details about the property, including the Access Code and its location. Upon arrival, you'll find a lockbox on the front gate, which contains a key specifically for your stay. The neighborhood Casa Calle Azul is nestled in Puerta Azul, a gated resort-style community known for its peaceful setting, beautiful walking paths, and curated amenities like tennis courts, pools, a fitness center, and a clubhouse. Whether you're relaxing on-site or heading out to explore, you're in one of the most desirable areas in La Quinta. Experience nearby the golf haven of PGA West, boasting six courses across 2,000 acres. During your stay, indulge in three public courses: Nicklaus Tournament, TPC Stadium, and Greg Norman. Beyond golf, La Quinta offers endless attractions. Discover the charm of Old Town La Quinta, shop the upscale boutiques of El Paseo in Palm Desert, or unwind at the prestigious Spa La Quinta. Outdoor lovers can enjoy bike paths, mountain hikes, or even a tram ride to 8,500 feet for breathtaking views. The culinary scene across La Quinta and the Coachella Valley is unmatched -- from Zagat-rated restaurants to local favorites. You're just minutes from the Polo Grounds, making this home a perfect retreat during events like Coachella, Stagecoach, the CareerBuilder Challenge, and the BNP Paribas Open Tennis Classic. Whether you're visiting for golf, music, food, or simply to unwind, Casa Calle Azul places you right in the heart of it all -- and we'd love to welcome you back again and again. Getting around For optimal transportation, a private car is recommended. Taxi services are available from Palm Springs airport, and both Ube

Effortlessly stylish and filled with sunshine, this south-facing, turnkey furnished Hacienda in Puerta Azul offers unobstructed mountain views, a private pool & spa, fire pit, ultimate privacy, and coveted short-term rental eligibility. Set in one of the community's prime locations, this 2BD/2.5BA (1,557 SF) residence enjoys all-day natural light perfect for laid-back desert living or investment versatility. Inside, the vibe is crisp and contemporary with high ceilings, abundant windows, and a layout designed for both comfort and separation. Two spacious primary suites, each with dual vanities, are positioned on opposite ends of the home—ideal for hosting guests in style. The open kitchen is equally functional and inviting, featuring granite slab counters, stainless steel appliances, bar seating, and a dreamy sink view. An airy dining area opens to the outdoors through glass sliders, extending your living space to a large wrap-around patio. Whether you're sipping coffee in the sun or lounging beneath the covered patio, the lush landscaping—dotted with blooming flowers and citrus trees—sets the tone for relaxation. Included in the lower monthly HOA's is access and use of the fitness center, a tennis court, community pools and spas and the club house. Whether you're exploring your first desert escape, seeking an income-generating opportunity, or completing a 1031 exchange, this turnkey home delivers on every front.
